Please note that after you delete your account:
1. You can no longer use this account to play;
2. You cannot retrieve your account, and any rights and interests under your account shall be deemed to be automatically waived by you;
3. We will no longer retain any of your information or will anonymize your information.

5. The accounts of other games associated with this account will also be deleted.
6. Your account information on other clients will also be cancelled.
Do you want to continue to delete your account?
100279.chinesesimplified:
请你特别请注意，注销账号后：
1.您不能再继续使用本账号进行游戏；
2.您不能找回账号，您账号下的任何权益视为您自动放弃；
3.我们也将不再保留您的任何信息或将对您的信息进行匿名化处理。
4.信息包扩账号信息、游戏日志、游戏装备等任何因使用本游戏服务而产生的数据。
5.与本账号关联的其他游戏的账号也会一同注销；
6.您在其他客户端的同账号信息也会注销。
您是否要继续注销账号？
